#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM377 12g"
msgid_plural "NM377s 12g"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture pistol, also nicknamed 'Last Hope'. Essentially a "
"factory-made one-shot short shotgun, more accurate than home-made ones, but "
"still only doing well in close-range. Developed in a few months before "
"cataclysm to earn money on common people's paranoia, it did well in that."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM379 9mm"
msgid_plural "NM377s 9mm"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture pistol, a small, light and cheap weapon designed for "
"self-defense. Holds 2 rounds, and every single one has to be inserted "
"manually, making reload difficult."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM338"
msgid_plural "NM338s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture laser pistol, brings the power of laser to a common "
"man. Uses charged battery packs, unlike most energy weapons out there."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM392 7x30mm"
msgid_plural "NM392s 7x30mm"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture six-shot revolver chambered for 7x30mm, made with low "
"cost and durability in mind."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM103 9mm"
msgid_plural "NM103s 9mm"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"First gun ever to be developed by Nimian's Manufacture, this lightweight "
"rifle is very accurate and durable, but clip size is very small as a result."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM302 .50"
msgid_plural "NM302s .50"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"This pistol, developed by Nimian's Manufacture in around 2038, employs "
"several creative ideas and lots of superalloy to make firing .50 BMG round "
"in a pistol worthwhile."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM322 .22"
msgid_plural "NM322s .22"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture .22 pistol. Small size of the round actually allowed "
"engineers to make the pistol hold more than 4 rounds, while also adding a "
"burst-fire mode."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json .\nm_weapons_military.json
