msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM380 .45"
msgid_plural "NM380s .45"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture .45 pistol. Advertised as 'sniper pistol', this little "
"beauty has anything a good marksman needs: an built-in scope, a stock that "
"can also be used as holster and incredible accuracy to boot. Holds only 4 "
"rounds though."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM380 7x30mm"
msgid_plural "NM380s 7x30mm"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 7x30mm pistol, copy of the .45 pistol that was adapted "
"to use Nimian own ammunition. Advertised as 'sniper pistol', this little "
"beauty has anything a good marksman needs: an built-in scope, a stock that "
"can also be used as holster and incredible accuracy to boot. Holds 6 rounds."
" Best to use with match rounds."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM323 5.56x45mm"
msgid_plural "NM323s 5.56x45mm"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture pistol, chambered for 5.56x45mm ammo. It's still more "
"accurate than most guns out there, and still lightweight, but light weight "
"still makes it hard to control recoil, and it only holds 3 bullets."
msgstr ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM333"
msgid_plural "NM333s"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture laser pistol, draws power from integrated plutonium "
"cell, so it can fire about 5.5 million times before discharging. The beam is"
" very weak though."
msgstr ""

